- create copy and modify keymap in idea settings
- run `python keymap.py <pato to the modified keymap> /path/to/src/main/resources/keymaps/nd.xml > updated.xml`
- run ediff updated.xml src/main/resources/keymaps/nd.xml and apply the changes
- bump version in src/main/resources/META-INF/plugin.xml
- commit
- create a tag (vNext)
- push commit and the tag
- run the buildPlugin gradle task
- publish new release based on the vNext tag with binary build/distributions/nd-keymap.zip
- bump versions in https://github.com/nd/ij-plugin-repo/blob/master/plugins.xml
- restart Idea to detect a new plugin version
